21:21.980 --> 21:23.880
You're actually worried what I think?

21:23.915 --> 21:27.976
Betty, I'm here because
I'm fooling around with my assistant.

21:28.020 --> 21:29.544
So, my point was,

21:29.588 --> 21:31.681
I'm not one
to pass judgment on anyone.

21:31.723 --> 21:34.055
Just give me a little heads up next time.

21:38.130 --> 21:40.462
