24:42.547 --> 24:44.276
No, stop, stop. You can't cancel on her.

24:44.316 --> 24:46.876
Why not? I'd rather go with you.

24:46.918 --> 24:49.352
That's also very sweet,
but you should take your mom.

24:49.387 --> 24:51.116
I can go later in the week.

24:51.156 --> 24:52.350
- You sure?
