25:23.054 --> 25:24.078
Oh.

25:25.190 --> 25:27.658
You have to kiss Lily?

25:27.692 --> 25:30.388
But I thought you liked this girl, right?

25:31.029 --> 25:33.361
- Isn't this a good thing?
- Yeah.

25:34.032 --> 25:39.163
We've just never rehearsed it,
