26:57.816 --> 26:59.613
Those for one of the actors?

26:59.651 --> 27:02.552
For the playwright.
We're seeing each other.

27:02.587 --> 27:05.886
- Zachary Boule? Really?
- Really.

27:07.058 --> 27:10.653
I mean, I was supposed to sit with him,
but he's bringing his mother instead.

27:10.695 --> 27:13.357
And I couldn't just not come,
so I used my press pass.

27:13.398 --> 27:15.866
Actually, I thought I'd get a better seat.

27:16.568 --> 27:19.128
Not that these are bad seats.
These are great seats.

27:19.170 --> 27:21.968
Let's just hope the play is
as good as that story.

27:27.579 --> 27:29.206
There he is.

27:31.683 --> 27:34.151
Zach. Zach.

27:35.887 --> 27:38.151
Hi. I made it.

27:56.541 --> 28:01.001
