when you kissed her.

34:12.283 --> 34:14.774
You wish. I definitely did it right.

34:14.819 --> 34:17.083
You just have to have
everyone seeing you all the time.

34:17.121 --> 34:19.315
Trust me,
they were looking at me anyway.

34:19.357 --> 34:22.815
- You are so in love with yourself.
- Wouldn't you be?

34:38.976 --> 34:40.375
I'm sorry.

34:58.429 --> 35:00.829
No.
Isn't that dress tacky?

35:00.865 --> 35:03.732
