35:03.768 --> 35:05.827
That dress is a no.

35:08.473 --> 35:11.271
- Hey, I'm home.
- Justin!

35:11.309 --> 35:13.368
- There's my star.
- Hey.

35:13.578 --> 35:14.670
Oh, my God.

35:14.712 --> 35:16.680
You're not gonna believe
what your Aunt Betty did.

35:16.714 --> 35:19.308
She punched that guy Zachary
at his premiere.

35:19.350 --> 35:21.250
Look, it's already on the Internet.

35:21.452 --> 35:23.545
Wow. That's crazy.

35:23.588 --> 35:26.819
I'm not proud of it,
but it did feel really good.

35:28.159 --> 35:30.389
Okay, well, good night.

35:30.428 --> 35:34.455
Hey, why are you rushing off to bed?
And why are you home so early?

35:34.499 --> 35:37.161
I thought you were gonna hang out
with Lily and what's-his-name.

35:37.735 --> 35:40.829
Austin. Yeah, I was.

35:41.772 --> 35:44.172
I'm just not feeling that great.

35:45.510 --> 35:48.377
I don't think I'm gonna go
to acting class tomorrow.

35:48.412 --> 35:49.674
Really?

35:52.283 --> 35:55.252
Must just be the excitement
from the night, huh?

35:55.553 --> 35:57.783
Yeah. Maybe.

36:03.161 --> 36:06.892
Man, teenagers and their mood swings.

36:06.931 --> 36:09.491
One minute he's up,
and the next minute...

36:12.236 --> 36:14.864
God, what's wrong with you?

36:17.875 --> 36:20.844
This whole time
I thought I was hiding him,

36:22.346 --> 36:24.246
and he was hiding me.

36:24.515 --> 36:28.611
And the worst part is, on some level,
I knew how this was gonna end.

36:28.653 --> 36:30.348
Come on, come on.

36:30.388 --> 36:32.822
You can't turn this
into something that it's not.

36:32.857 --> 36:34.222
It's true.

36:34.258 --> 36:36.249
Every time I feel like
I'm moving forward,

36:36.294 --> 36:37.989
someone reminds me that

36:38.963 --> 36:42.490
I'm still just the dork
with glasses and braces.

36:43.067 --> 36:46.298
Yeah, but those braces are coming off
any day now.

36:46.337 --> 36:48.897
Yeah, but what if nothing changes?

36:50.741 --> 36:54.142
- Then I'll have nothing to blame.
- Honey,

36:55.313 --> 36:57.110
you've got to stop.

36:57.148 --> 36:59.742
Somehow, you got it in your head

37:00.184 --> 37:02.118
that this is your story.

37:03.454 --> 37:05.684
But you got to let that go.

37:05.723 --> 37:09.318
It's time to come up
with a whole new story for yourself.

37:09.727 --> 37:11.524
You are who you are,

37:12.463 --> 37:14.192
and the sooner that
you're okay with that,

37:14.232 --> 37:17.258
the sooner that you see what I see,

37:17.902 --> 37:20.029
the happier you're gonna be.

37:20.071 --> 37:22.062
I swear to God.

37:32.049 --> 37:33.346
Okay.

37:35.253 --> 37:36.277
Oh.

37:36.320 --> 37:39.619
- Hey, did you get my text?
- No.

37:40.625 --> 37:43.389
I've been kind of avoiding texts all day.

37:43.427 --> 37:46.988
Well, I finally talked to my mom.
We really got into it again.

37:47.031 --> 37:50.194
I am in such a bad mood.

37:50.835 --> 37:53.633
- I'm sorry, Daniel.
- Big plans?

37:54.538 --> 37:56.233
You know what?

37:56.274 --> 37:58.868
I'm not sure
I'm up for our kind of plans tonight.

37:59.744 --> 38:01.302
Okay.

38:02.513 --> 38:05.346
It's cool. You mind if I just hang out?

38:06.017 --> 38:09.145
I don't really feel like
being alone right now.

38:09.587 --> 38:10.645
Come on in.

38:10.688 --> 38:12.986
I'll grab a couple
of Marc's 64-calorie beers.

38:13.024 --> 38:15.049
- You want one?
- No, I'm good.

38:29.173 --> 38:30.697
You're late.

38:30.741 --> 38:33.471
Sorry, Willie. About yesterday...

38:33.511 --> 38:36.537
It's fine. Turns out you were right.

38:37.782 --> 38:39.443
It was good for me.

38:39.850 --> 38:41.340
- Really?
- Yes.

38:41.786 --> 38:44.050
I had an epiphany last night.

38:49.427 --> 38:50.894
That angel.

38:53.931 --> 38:56.798
That sweet, wheezing angel

38:56.834 --> 39:01.965
said something to me last night
that made me reevaluate my priorities.

39:04.141 --> 39:07.406
I'm wasting my life, Marc.
What am I doing?

39:07.778 --> 39:10.611
Working at a fashion magazine
day and night,

39:10.648 --> 39:12.741
and for what? A paycheck?

39:13.317 --> 39:16.753
A meager percentage
of some dwindling bottom line?

39:18.556 --> 39:20.421
I know what I want,

39:20.458 --> 39:22.153
<i>and it's not Mode.</i>

39:24.962 --> 39:26.395
It's not?

39:29.533 --> 39:31.125
It's Meade.

39:31.168 --> 39:32.965
I want the whole damn company.

39:33.003 --> 39:35.198
And this time,
I'm not gonna dance around Claire.

39:35.239 --> 39:38.731
No more compromising with Daniel.
No more Nice Willie.

39:39.477 --> 39:41.411
This has been Nice Willie?

39:41.445 --> 39:44.903
If I'm gonna die,
I'm gonna die with the most toys.

39:50.621 --> 39:54.182
- Betty.
- Oh, no. Look at your face.

39:54.225 --> 39:55.783
It's okay, I deserved it.

39:55.826 --> 39:57.885
I came by to say thank you
for sending me the profile.

39:58.362 --> 40:00.887
It was surprisingly nice.
Kind of expected you to trash me.

40:00.931 --> 40:03.263
No, I would never do that.

40:03.300 --> 40:06.497
Aside from the occasional punching
and sneaking around,

40:06.537 --> 40:09.062
I like to keep it professional.

40:09.106 --> 40:10.937
I'm glad you liked the article.

40:10.975 --> 40:12.135
Betty.

40:13.844 --> 40:17.371
I really am sorry, and I really like you.

40:18.182 --> 40:20.776
And this might be
presumptuous of me to ask,

40:21.452 --> 40:24.853
but is there any chance
you might give me another shot?

40:25.756 --> 40:29.214
No. Thanks, but no.

40:29.260 --> 40:32.855
I think it's time for me
to try something different.

40:32.897 --> 40:34.694
But I'll see you around.

40:43.140 --> 40:45.005
- Hey.
Hi.

40:46.177 --> 40:48.839
- Have you seen Austin?
- No.

40:48.879 --> 40:50.073
I'm sorry I'm late.

40:50.114 --> 40:53.083
Some days,
it's just hard to get out of bed.

40:53.117 --> 40:56.917
You're actors, you'll see.
Okay, let's begin.

40:58.189 --> 41:00.623
- Yeah?
- Shouldn't we wait for Austin?

41:00.658 --> 41:03.718
Oh, no.
Austin will no longer be joining us.

41:03.761 --> 41:06.389
He dropped out of class this morning.

41:06.931 --> 41:12.961
Okay, so, today, we're gonna talk about
having a physical life on the stage.

41:35.059 --> 41:39.086
Hi, my name is Betty Suarez,
and I'm looking for a new orthodontist.

41:39.129 --> 41:42.826
I was wondering if Dr. Frankel is
taking any new patients.

41:44.201 --> 41:47.728
I've been wearing braces
for over four years now.

41:49.306 --> 41:53.242
Wednesday? That would be great.

